{"word":"ἔμβιος","slug":"ἔμβιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n33994\" key=\"e)/mbios\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἔμβῐ-ος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, <sense id=\"n33994.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">having life</tr_>, [<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Ζηνὸς] ἐργαζομένου ἔμβια τὰ ὑπὸ τῷ αἰθέρι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0638.tlg004:2:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philostr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Her.\">Her.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.19</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tenacious of life, established</tr_>, of trees which will bear transplanting, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg002:5:6:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ CP\">CP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.6.5</biblScope> </bibl>; of cuttings, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg002:3:5:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.5.3</biblScope> </bibl> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Comp.\">Comp.</a></gram> </gramGrp>); but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἰ σπέρμα ἔ. γένοιτο</foreign> if the seed should <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">germinate</tr_>, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg002:5:4:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.4.5</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1147.tlg001:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Antipho Soph.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸ ἔ</foreign>. their <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">living and growing</tr_>, of trees, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg002:13:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ VH\">VH</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.1</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n33994.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ ἔ. ὑγρότης</foreign> the moisture <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">necessary to life</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg002:1:1:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ CP\">CP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.1.3</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αἷμα ἔ. τῇ γῇ πινόμενον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1600.tlg001:1:24\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philostr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Im.\">Im.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.24</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n33994.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lasting one's whole life</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔ. τιμωρία</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0385.tlg001:78:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.C.\">D.C.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">78.12</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n33994.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔ. γενέσθαι</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">recover consciousness</tr_> after a swoon, <bibl n=\"urn:ct